      "term": "antinomical",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "C2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "adjective",
          "definition": "Involving or showing a contradiction between two principles or ideas that both seem reasonable",
          "examples": [
            "The philosopher explored the antinomical relationship between freedom and responsibility.",
